---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Markdown from '../components/Markdown.astro';

const heroContent = `
# AI-Powered Project-Based Learning

Transform education through meaningful, real-world learning missions designed with AI integration at the core. PBL Future Labs empowers educators and students to move beyond traditional worksheets and unlock authentic, community-connected learning experiences.

## Our Vision

We believe project-based learning—enhanced by AI—breaks down barriers, saves teachers time, elevates student voice, and connects learning to real-world impact.

**Learning missions** are the heart of our approach: thoughtfully designed projects that combine academic rigor with authentic problem-solving, powered by AI tools that adapt to each learner's needs.

### Explore PBL Future Labs

- **Learning Missions**: Discover curated missions aligned with standards
- **Project Examples**: See real student work and inspiring case studies
- **Mission Builder**: Create your own AI-assisted learning missions
- **Micro Credentials**: Earn badges for project mastery
`;
---

<Layout title="Welcome to PBL Future Labs">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <Markdown content={heroContent} class="prose prose-invert max-w-none mb-12" />
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <a href="/missions" class="card bg-blue-900/40 border border-blue-400/50 hover:border-blue-400 transition p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Explore Learning Missions</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-200">Browse hundreds of learning missions designed for authentic impact</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/projects" class="card bg-purple-900/40 border border-purple-400/50 hover:border-purple-400 transition p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">See Real Projects</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-200">Discover inspiring student work and real-world applications</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/builder" class="card bg-pink-900/40 border border-pink-400/50 hover:border-pink-400 transition p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Build a Mission</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-200">Create custom learning missions with AI assistance</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/credentials" class="card bg-teal-900/40 border border-teal-400/50 hover:border-teal-400 transition p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Earn Credentials</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-200">Unlock micro-credentials demonstrating project mastery</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
